messed up over it.

09:06.630 --> 09:10.467
Yeah. I never knew your husband.
I understand he was a fine man.

09:10.551 --> 09:13.554
Yes, he was.

09:15.430 --> 09:18.892
Well, I don't know how you
feel about therapy, but...

09:18.976 --> 09:21.770
If you think Mike needs somebody to
talk to, I know a gentleman over...

09:21.854 --> 09:24.857
