Mr. Collins. He can talk to me.

09:28.193 --> 09:30.112
Do you think he will, though?

09:30.237 --> 09:34.616
I'm sorry, Wayne. I didn't know
you had anybody in here.

09:34.700 --> 09:37.077
- Oh, hi.
- Ruby wasn't at her desk.

09:37.160 --> 09:40.497
Yeah, she's out sick today.
Mrs. Wilson, this is Jessica King,

09:40.581 --> 09:42.541
- my fiancee.
- Nice to meet you.

09:42.624 --> 09:45.252
You too.

09:45.335 --> 09:48.964
We're just going to be
a couple of minutes. Okay.

09:49.006 --> 09:52.801
I gotta go anyway.
I got people waiting.

09:52.885 --> 09:54.887
Thanks a lot,
Mr. Collins.

09:54.970 --> 09:59.141
- I'm real sorry about all this.
- Oh, it's my job.

09:59.183 --> 10:02.144
He's just a boy,
that's all.

10:04.354 --> 10:07.357
You're not that Wilson that's
a fortune-teller, are you?

10:07.441 --> 10:09.234
