be real happy together.

11:14.007 --> 11:18.220
- Hey, how you gettin' along today?
- I'm fine, Buddy.

11:18.303 --> 11:22.432
Except the fact I can't keep my car
door from just flying right open.

11:22.516 --> 11:24.893
Have you got the time
to fix it?

11:24.977 --> 11:29.106
