a negative thought,

13:37.442 --> 13:39.361
am I gonna die?

13:39.444 --> 13:41.613
No.

13:41.655 --> 13:44.992
You're not gonna die.

13:45.075 --> 13:47.369
You're not gonna die,
Buddy.

13:49.621 --> 13:54.835
Oh, my God!
Oh, my God! Oh, my God!

13:54.918 --> 13:57.337
Oh, look...

13:57.421 --> 14:00.424
Okay. Well, thank you.
