Something's happened to her.

16:26.778 --> 16:31.033
What's happened?
She okay?

16:31.116 --> 16:34.328
Well, no, she's not, ma'am.

16:34.411 --> 16:37.122
Ma'am, I promise.
I'll just take a minute.

16:39.833 --> 16:43.462
All right.
Come on.

17:01.480 --> 17:04.398
What's happened is she's getting
her head filled full of shit...

17:04.483 --> 17:06.777
by a goddamn
Satan worshipper.

17:06.859 --> 17:10.696
Or a damn good con artist,
one of the two.

17:10.781 --> 17:14.867
