20:07.207 --> 20:09.835
- Valerie!
- Oh, Annie! Annie, it's him! No!

20:09.918 --> 20:11.837
- Calm down. I'll call the law.
- No. No.

20:11.920 --> 20:14.464
No, Annie, no! If you're
my friend, you won't! No!

20:16.175 --> 20:19.261
