20:31.732 --> 20:36.153
- You let her go!
- All right! All right!

20:38.322 --> 20:41.950
- Get in!
- Mike, you stay there!

20:42.034 --> 20:44.161
What did I fucking tell you?

20:44.244 --> 20:47.247
All right!

20:50.667 --> 20:52.711
