23:20.609 --> 23:23.862
- Do we pay him now or...
- I sign for it later.

23:23.946 --> 23:26.073
Is it good?

23:27.199 --> 23:29.535
- Annie, there he is.
- Who?

23:29.618 --> 23:32.830
That guy I... That guy I was
telling you about. Look at him.

23:32.913 --> 23:36.792
He's right over there by the bar.
Don't he look like Antonio Banderas?

23:36.875 --> 23:40.337
Oh, my God! He saw me! Shit!
